              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>I photograph live music and cover shows across the UK. This is where those nights get written up. Reviews of shows I have shot, shows I am about to cover, and music I am listening to. It also brings together two regular audio slots I contribute to: The Portrait Guy podcast with Guy Lloyd and my segment on Slack City Radio.</p>"
              }
