              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>I appear as a regular guest on The Portrait Guy podcast hosted by Guy Lloyd. We talk portrait photography, the business side of shooting people, gear, mindset and the things that actually make a difference when you are in front of a client.</p><p>Episode notes, links and my take on the conversations we have are collected here.</p><p><a href='/stories/category/the-portrait-guy'>Episode notes and links</a></p>"
